The paper deals with the field of human-computer interaction, which is primarily covered under the sub-category of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms for classification, which falls under the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of EMG signals for emotion recognition can also be categorized under cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper involves the use of signal processing techniques, which can be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Finally, the paper involves the use of Support Vector Machine algorithm, which is a popular algorithm in the field of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
